            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. Gard[en] ¶ 21. Sept. 1857. ¶ Dear Mr Archer ¶  ¶ I am much obliged for your kind attention to Major General M'Arthurs request. If I am not too much intruding on you, will you let me hav...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">57.09.21</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Henry Archer</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">2/137/1, Archer papers, University of Melbourne Archives.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. Gard[en]<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition </seg>— MS damaged.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">21. Sept. 1857.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Mr Archer</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am much obliged for your kind attention to Major General M'Arthurs request. If I am not too much intruding on you, will you let me have one or two small parcels more of the <seg style="color: #000000; ">Zuly</seg>
               <seg style="color: #000000; ">
                  <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">Zulu?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style="color: #000000; "> Imphee</seg>?</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I send you 12 packages of Cotton seed, which you probably can distribute without expense to the applicants for the <name key="Holcus">Holcus</name> simultaneously.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[I]<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition </seg>— MS damaged.</p>
               </note> am sorry, that your name was omitted as a donor to the gardens. You will however observe, that I said, minor gifts had been received from other gentlemen.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">B57.09.01.</p>
               </note> Previous to my taking the responsibility of administrating this establishment, the books were but laxely kept, and thus I am aware of the incompleteness of the list of Mr Dallachi.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have however alluded to the <name key="Holcus">Holcus</name> as distributed th[anks] to your <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">assiduity</hi>
               </seg> in [the] paper on introductions of plants, […]<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">illegible </seg>— MS damaged.</p>
               </note> at the last meeting of our institute.<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The reading of M's paper, B58.05.02, was postponed at the monthly meeting of the Philosophical Institute, 2 September, until 30 September (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">Transactions of the Philosophical Institute of Victoria</seg>
                     <seg style="">, vol. 2</seg> (1858), pp. xl, xliii). In the paper M remarked: 'Amongst grains I may also briefly allude to the Chinese Sugar-grass (<name key="Holcus">Holcus</name> sacharatus), of which the Caffir variety has been lately distributed throughout the country by Mr. Archer's assiduity, under a desire of adding to the vegetable treasures of the colony' (p. 96).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Is it not possible to get through your friends abroad occasionally a few seeds of <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">trees</hi>
               </seg> or <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">shrubs</hi>
               </seg> of rarer kinds, for which we would be able to offer always an good equivalent. We do not care much for <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">annual</hi>
               </seg> seeds, unless from useful species</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Obediently yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Holcus">Holcus</name>
            </p>
         </div>
